                <p class="section-subtitle">Applied Microeconomics with Focus on Policy Evaluation</p>
            </div>

            <div class="research-interests">
                <div class="interests-grid">
                    <div class="interest-card">
                        <h3>Economics of Education</h3>
                        <p>Analyzing the impacts of educational policies and reforms on long-term outcomes, with particular focus on compulsory schooling laws and their effects on social attitudes and behaviors.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="interest-card">
                        <h3>Labour Economics</h3>
                        <p>Examining labor market transitions, the role of internships in career development, and the effects of educational interventions on employment outcomes and earnings.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="interest-card">
                        <h3>Health Economics</h3>
                        <p>Investigating the health impacts of environmental policies, particularly the effectiveness of pollution control measures on population health outcomes.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
